Summary: Small Oval Light Drifting In Sky In Broad Day Light.
divs: Sighting DetailsHey, i was just outside in my backyard trying to get some sun while doing paper work when i decided to get up and make myself comfy. While i was doing this, a small object in the sky (star size) caught my attention. I looked at it thinking it was a plane straight away then i noticed that it was moving pretty fast and it was an oval white object. I viewed it for about 10 seconds then ran inside to get my camera, and when i came out it was gone. While i was trying to record the sky incase any more objects came, my camera then died and started going weird. Now my camera doesn't work.
